snippet.title: 2076 Midway Multiverse
snippet.description:
2076: Midway Multiverse is a side-scrolling shooter where you manipulate the environment thanks to the innovative use of VR technology.  Take control of your space combat ship and defeat the Nazi Galactic Empire once and for all!

More information: https://www.ivanovichgames.com/2076/
Steam link: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1508280/2076__Midway_Multiverse/
Oculus Quest demo: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/4504829629531931
